2. `server/index.js` — Handle `set_name` WebSocket message type
3. `client/index.html` — Add nickname input HTML element + CSS
4. `client/client.js` — Fix name label rendering + nickname input JS logic
5. `test/game.test.js` — Add nickname validation tests

